ifplugd (0.20-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * new upstream
  * scripts go to /etc/apm/scripts.d, _not_ /etc/apm/script.d
    (closes: #219196, #219488)
  * remove dynamically created conf files in postrm script
    (closes: #219489)
